msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh...<2.pa> So you heard me humming, eh?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"I'm Eryck.<3.pa> I'm traveling the world\n"
"on a journey of self-discovery.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>I'm heading for <5.se_co>Zora's Domain<6.re_co> now...<7.pa>\n"
"but I'm lost. I was just about to give up.\n"
"\n"
"But then, like, <8.pa>I heard a voice...<9.pa>\n"
"coming from the <10.se_co>north tower<11.re_co>...\n"
"\n"
"<12.so>Crossing the <13.se_co>Rutala River<14.re_co> would be next\n"
"to impossible, though...<15.ch>"
