msgctxt "talk03"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.se_co>Zora's Domain<3.re_co> is home of the Zora.<4.pa>\n"
"It's a town in <5.se_co>Lanayru<6.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"But crossing the <7.se_co>Rutala River<8.re_co>\n"
"is impossible.\n"
"\n"
"<9.so>It's a hard place to get to, so I just\n"
"gave up altogether."
