"<1.so>If you continue north from here, on the\n"
"other side of the <2.se_co>Rutala River<3.re_co>, <4.pa>you can\n"
"see a huge tower on the opposite bank.\n"
"<5.so>I thought I heard a voice coming from\n"
"the top of that tower.<6.pa> I wonder if\n"
"someone's up there."
