msgid ""
"<1.so><2.se_co>Rutala River<3.re_co> is the widest river\n"
"in <4.se_co>Lanayru<5.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"You'd be risking your life if you tried to\n"
"swim across it...\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>If you want to go north of it, you'll have\n"
"to walk patiently to <7.se_co>Linebeck Island<8.re_co> in\n"
"the east so you can circumvent it."
msgstr ""

